OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with clear periods. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,8,Facross all parts with variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,12,Fspreading eastwards across all parts,
OL,13,Fbut dry in the east in the morning.
OL,14,FMild in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAfter a
OL,17,Fchilly start on Friday it will be a
OL,18,Fdry and sunny day. Dry and bright on
OL,19,FSaturday but clouding over later.
OL,20,FCloudy with occasional rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
